      <title>[리빙포인트] 뻑뻑한 지퍼엔 립밤</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/12/07/CBRMB6T4AJFSVBULWCLXUENUC4/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/national_general/2025/12/07/CBRMB6T4AJFSVBULWCLXUENUC4/</guid>
      <dc:creator>조선일보</dc:creator>
      <description/>
